# LLM Provider Configuration
# Set LLM_PROVIDER to either "ollama" or "gpt" to switch between providers
# Default is "ollama" if not specified

# For Ollama (default):
# LLM_PROVIDER=ollama

# For GPT-4:
# LLM_PROVIDER=gpt
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here

# Example usage:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Uncomment and set the desired provider
# 3. For GPT, set your OpenAI API key
# 4. The system will automatically use the configured provider